{"tid":1585950,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"去完個旅行返來咩都唔同曬","createTime":"2019-09-21T18:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T12:16:41.000Z","uid":260114,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f4fa1627e35c9c6863cec835027a56349c38f4bc","tid":1585950,"uid":260114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:07:51.000Z","msg":"有冇人有咁嘅經歷，本來同班人好好朋友咁<br />\n佢哋去完旅行返來就咩都唔同曬<br />\n開始所有聚會冇你份，有咩就佢地開心講<br />\n你就冇份知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本來之後都可以扮冇嘢，但我又戇戇鳩䲪咁出左個令*佢地其中一個*唔開心嘅post，就開始來料<br />\n齊齊開post屌鳩我，咁今次我衰仔啦 知道之後即刻say曬sorry ，扮撚曬狗咁話之後都唔會做。<br />\n你老味，我同D fd呻下仲要比佢地mon post <br />\n又開始屌䲪我，冇撚野好講<br />\n原本好地地，係我戇鳩鳩扮大方比佢地繼續follow<br />\n搞撚到咁係我嘅錯 係我戇鳩鳩 <br />\n依架返學仲要面阻阻 <br />\n我要點撚樣做呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6431997135ae45c86ff492e902e9fb59153d424","tid":1585950,"uid":260114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:21:18.000Z","msg":"本來好好地做咩搞成咁"},{"pid":"cd3e389727cab2ba396d9556b7b6dffec81c4539","tid":1585950,"uid":260114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:22:34.000Z","msg":"個陣冇同你地去grad trip 係因為講左同屋企人去旅行 你地又唔係唔知"},{"pid":"2c584df728fd936e30eea157e7baa0ebdb56f910","tid":1585950,"uid":128204,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:23:22.000Z","msg":"唔撚知你講緊乜"},{"pid":"f7209b0b89ffdbf10257cbbd16343f03cd6aa027","tid":1585950,"uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:23:57.000Z","msg":"Grow up"},{"pid":"acd56f181d4941687f6fd6dcb9e8028452d718c9","tid":1585950,"uid":260114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c584df728fd936e30eea157e7baa0ebdb56f910","tid":1585950,"uid":128204,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:23:22.000Z","msg":"唔撚知你講緊乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"我都唔撚知"},{"pid":"52c26fe5133f670054abf589f35baad451b3349d","tid":1585950,"uid":260114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi